NLquery: For each Internet Service(sid), find the most frequently used version among all Base Models that utilize it. If multiple versions have the same highest frequency, you may return any one of them.

LLM_returned_SQL_query: WITH version_counts AS (SELECT sid, version, COUNT(*) AS freq, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION by sid ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS rn FROM BaseModels GROUP BY sid, version) SELECT sid, version, freq FROM version_counts WHERE rn = 1;
